Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.75,0:00:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Unmovable Sovereign, Ozen the Immovable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This irredeemable lesson of hers\Nis a trial before setting off anew...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.42,0:00:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It is "survival training" to help these children stay alive\Nas they make their way through the world of the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Spend ten days here with the equipment you've got.\NShow me you're able to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure not to go beyond that Pillar Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll consider that as trying to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm heading back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best to protect this girl\Nso that she doesn't return to being a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, you can't use that thing for these ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My Incinerator?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and use it if you want to get Riko killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you fire it, no matter how you push yourself,\Nyou always faint after around ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's a full two hours until you wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try leaving a helpless child on her own\Nin the second layer for two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder just how she'll be torn to shreds and eaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, when you really do have to use it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,go all out to make sure whatever it is\Ndoesn't come after you again in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter your opponent or whatever lies in the vicinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,when the time comes, don't hesitate or show any mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, your adventure will be over\Nin the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Daremo ga sakaraezu ni mogutteiku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono me o tomoshibi yori kagayakasete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mezasu saki wa fukaku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Massugu ni mayoikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuchiaketa naraku no wana
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinjitsu no ato o oikakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ima kotae ga mitsukaru nara zenbu nakushitemo ii
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono koe o hanasanai youni kodama ga mada hibiiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rashinban wa zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yami o sashita mama
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nigeba no nai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sore ga noroi demo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodou wa honmono
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nidoto akogare wa tomaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, we need to look for some water...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A-ah, Riko, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great. We found some water!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Think it's okay to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are rohanas,\Na kind of insect that only lives in clean water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In what way is that thing docile?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Around here, the animals have regressed eyes,\Nso they should be susceptible to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If we build a fire, I think they'll keep their distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Susceptible to light," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go look for some insect-repelling plants...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko is certainly plucky,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but her body can't keep up with what she wants to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And that boy Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, where are you?\NAlthough his body is extraordinarily resilient,\Nhe's constantly losing his nerves...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Although his body is extraordinarily resilient,\Nhe's constantly losing his nerves...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and is slow to make decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!\Nand is slow to make decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This despite the fact he's a mechanical doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If they die now, it just means\Nthey didn't have what it takes to go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, you're strong, but your body is light...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll have to devise a plan\Nif we're going to catch that hippo thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, maybe I could extend my arm\Nto bind it to a tree or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then let's lead it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is it? It stinks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dung from a female and some tree bark.\NI tore off a piece that's covered in pheromones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this to lure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it gets close to you, Reg,\Nwe'll blind it with our glow-stones!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it will work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine! Let's just try our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it now! Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Be it an immature body or weak psyche,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,they won't be showing real changes\Nin those areas any time soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But, just as you predicted, they're making\Nenormous progress in the things they're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are two of them, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's best that they learn to depend on one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Depend on one another," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who attacked you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait! I'll annihilate those punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Ozen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You giving up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing, Ozen!\NA whole field of Flowers of Fortitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't even feel like we're in the middle\Nof the netherworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Torka from my squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I got married to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ozen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind giving me a bit of time alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How incredibly maddening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that no sooner than\NTorka quickly passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,even the baby was stillborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some nerve to leave the delivery to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That dumb face and you come along, and just when Lyza\Nhad finally mellowed out, she gets treated like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How maddening...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to see Lyza in such a state.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much strength left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:09:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'll just leave this thing behind here\Nand carry the Bell up with Lyza...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief, I've taken on another burden now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a strong sense of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With this we should be able to make it through\Nthe remaining five days!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow... it feels like ages since we were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually been 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you are quite amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I started crying right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Any further out than the Seeker Camp\Nand it's almost completely dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and Master left and went back home by herself\Nsomewhere along the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Marulk, you know, even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Near the end when I got separated from Riko,\NI was feeling so hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, so that happens to even you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me feel a bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry? I'll bring you something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's already been ten days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, the pain I was feeling\Nfrom Ozen's thrashing is gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the "Riko Hodgepodge Stew" did the trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My rehabilitation is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This pattern...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it always like that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,seems I never put on any muscle...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg! Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Master is saying that now that you're back,\Nwe should all have a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Spending 10 days there, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was pretty hectic, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back at it now,\Nit feels like it was over in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't stay in the deep layers\Nif you don't want to kill those who're waiting for you"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an old saying like that, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One's sense of time goes mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's particularly striking in the depths of the fifth layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I had intended to stay down there a few weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but when I returned to the surface,\Na few months had passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Such occurrences are common...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So that rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is true, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no rumor. I'm telling you flat out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, only those with strange tastes -
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,basically just us White Whistles -\Nwould try living in the deep layers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That saying I mentioned that\Nif you stay there for a really long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone who's waiting for you will probably die,\Nis somewhat of an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you probably think it has nothing to do with you\Nsince you're making a journey of no return...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But the problem is that\Nwe can't even estimate the extent
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to which this "madness" manifests\Nin the sixth and seventh layers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that perhaps not as much time\Nas we all think has actually passed for Lyza.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years on the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we assume that only a few years have passed\Nat the bottom of the netherworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,don't you get the feeling there's a very good chance\Nshe's alive and well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even so, you should do your best\Nnot to stay in the fifth layer for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And why would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So that you don't bump into\Nany of the other White Whistles...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The depths' fifth layer, the Sea of Corpses,\Nis as deep as humans can go and return alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose some of them are there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:14:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sovereign of Guidance, Wakuna the Chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sovereign of Mystery, Srajo the Mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sovereign of Dawn, Bondrewd the Novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the other three\Nwho are down in the Abyss now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Among them... Bondrewd in particular\Nis an out-and-out scoundrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not kind like I am, so you better be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of Lyza, I also have something\NI'm curious about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The slip in the sealed letter that said:\N"At the netherworld's bottom, I'll be waiting"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who wrote that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written overly large in crooked penmanship,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,using old nether glyphs\Nwithout any of the simplified forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, the paper it's on isn't even paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an unknown Relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks all worn out, but it really surprised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing can't be ripped even with my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is waiting down\Nat the netherworld's bottom together with Lyza?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,both of you, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Blaze Reap... the everlasting pickax.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a specialized weapon with which\NLyza the Annihilator spilled much blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stuck in the ground like a grave marker\Nin that cluster of Eternal Fortunes I spoke of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The everlasting gunpowder inside it is fine,\Nbut the outer casing is in bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It can only be used a few more times at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:16:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a piece of junk\Nthat occasionally misfired even back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about Lyza here,\Nso I bet she's already found a new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you how to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be able to act as an alternative\Nto that Incinerator of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You really mean that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm about to tell you\Nmust not be shared with anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With those words, Ozen spoke of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the numerous secrets that had been transmitted from\Nthe last dives of many generations of White Whistles,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,which are passed down by word of mouth\Namong only themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, those were the very deepest voices of Abyss\Nthat people are capable of carrying to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard about the cryptic device\Nfor traversing the fifth layer's "Sea"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,About how a white whistle's timbre acts as a key\Nto activate a certain class of Relics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:17:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,About the mysterious ring of the seventh layer\Nthat only a few White Whistles are said to have seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When Ozen said she hates deceiving children,\Nshe was telling the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,From start to finish,\Nthis monster sitting before us held nothing back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're already heading out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be lonely around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's cold of Ozen not to come see you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already given us so much, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's taught us many things...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be right to ask any more of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite all appearances, you're quite humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cut that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Marulk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you take care now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I find it hard to say this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you come back and say, "It's impossible, after all,"\Nit'd be oh so nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Marulk...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen off all kinds of people\Nwho leave on journeys they won't return from...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But... today is the saddest I've ever felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg and that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, they were quick\Nto pick up on cave-raiding techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, I didn't want to let them go\Nuntil more memories come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, nothing I can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Lyza?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That baby crawled toward the Abyss\Nthe moment she was let out of the Vessel,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,which is pretty darn creepy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:19:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, she's monstrously energetic now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My apprentice is already fed up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just splendid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You have an apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,His name's Jiruo. You've met him before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that rash and shameless kid\Nwho turned down my invitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer the Sovereign of Annihilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that she hasn't dropped dead or been killed\Nmeans you're doing a good job keeping her hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If it ever came to light that she's your daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd be kidnapped by ruffians\Nwhile you're down in the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And, if you're lucky, she'd be held hostage,\Nbut if you're unlucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. My apprentice is top grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,However, be that as it may...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko is incredibly precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter the Relic or whatever else of mine\NI offer as payment, it's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to a whole heap of priceless things,\Nthat girl is alive right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I continue to stay with her, I'm liable to take\NRiko's right to set off on adventures away from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and I myself will likely become separated from the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that happens, I'm heading out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So that my girl is free to choose whatever path...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what you're glossing over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it true that you simply\Ngot an urge to see the bottom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ozen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If Riko once again sets out to reach the bottom\Nand in doing so comes to stand before you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean about how she's a living corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,About how much of a miracle it took\Nto make it so that she's able to move at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,About how to tackle the magnificent adventures\Nthat are waiting for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:21:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain. Do that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if we're just talking about\Nsending her on to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief... How irredeemable...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How very irredeemable...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Inverted Forest... It's so far above us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sora ni ukanderu hikaru nami o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanete niji no hashi o kakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaui ashiba, suberu slope
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.83,0:22:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako to mirai no michishirube
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.25,0:22:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi no hidarite, boku no migite o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunaide tsunagete hajimeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsumo soba ni iru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako mo ima mo mirai mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakara mayowazu ni aruiteikou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.88,0:23:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Irotoridori no yume kasanete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashita wa doko ni mukau
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi to issho ni iretara, sekai wa kagayakidasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Saihate no chi ni saku hana o sagasou
